Trade/Device Name(s): DAVID One Step Home Use Pregnancy Test Strip
DAVID One Step Home Use Pregnancy Test Cassette
DAVID One Step Home Use Pregnancy Test Midstream
DAVID One Step Prescription Pregnancy Test Strip

Methodologies: Qualitative solid-phase double antibody sandwich assay
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for DAVID One Step pregnancy test devices (strip, cassette, midstream) for qualitative detection of hCG in urine to aid in early pregnancy detection
Indications for Use Summary: Qualitative detection of hCG in urine to aid early detection of pregnancy, for over-the-counter (home use) and prescription use in formats including strip, cassette, and midstream; results as early as five days before expected period
